      "message": "[Critical] Line 66: `isPluginOverwrite: Body !\u003d\u003d OriginalBody` treats missing or empty OriginalBody as a modification, so messages whose OriginalBody role is unset can incorrectly show \u0027Modified by extension\u0027 and the original toggle. Gate this on OriginalBody actually being present before comparing.\n```suggestion\n    property bool isPluginOverwrite: OriginalBody !\u003d\u003d \"\" \u0026\u0026 Body !\u003d\u003d OriginalBody\n```",
