      "message": "[Critical] Line 80: The edited-message branch assumes PreviousBodies[0].body always exists. If the model marks a message edited before history is populated, or history is unavailable, toggling \u0027Show original\u0027 will throw a QML TypeError and break delegate rendering. Guard the access and either hide the toggle when there is no previous body or fall back safely.\n```suggestion\n                if (showOriginal) {\n                    if (isPluginOverwrite)\n                        return OriginalBody;\n                    return PreviousBodies.length \u003e 0 ? PreviousBodies[0].body : Body;\n                }\n```",
