      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Critical] Line 80: The original/previous body is rendered directly, bypassing the existing ParsedBody/MessagesAdapter.parseMessage path used for normal messages. That can regress hyperlink preview/parsing behavior and may expose raw markup/control content differently from current messages. Route the selected body through the same parsing/sanitization path instead of returning raw OriginalBody/PreviousBodies[0].body. For example:\n```suggestion\n                const displayBody \u003d showOriginal\n                        ? (isPluginOverwrite ? OriginalBody : (PreviousBodies.length \u003e 0 ? PreviousBodies[0].body : Body))\n                        : Body;\n                if (displayBody !\u003d\u003d \"\" \u0026\u0026 ParsedBody.length \u003d\u003d\u003d 0) {\n                    MessagesAdapter.parseMessage(Id, displayBody, UtilsAdapter.getAppValue(Settings.DisplayHyperlinkPreviews), rootDelegate.colorUrl, bubble.color);\n                    return \"\";\n                }\n```",
      "revId": "9c155ed72795658eaa7759392da8029f0533d52c",
